## Changes

### 1. Daily Prompt Scrolling ([lib/screens/today_screen.dart](file:///Users/aniruddhmodi/Documents/Aniruddh/Extracurricular/flutter-app/the_30sec_journal/lib/screens/today_screen.dart))
- **Change**: Updated the `SingleChildScrollView` physics in [_buildFieldPage](file:///Users/aniruddhmodi/Documents/Aniruddh/Extracurricular/flutter-app/the_30sec_journal/lib/screens/today_screen.dart#453-649).
- **Logic**:
    -   When the keyboard is **open** (`viewInsets.bottom > 0`), the scroll physics is set to `BouncingScrollPhysics`. This allows the user to scroll the content up so the text box is visible.
    -   When the keyboard is **closed**, it reverts to `NeverScrollableScrollPhysics` to prioritize the custom vertical swipe gestures for page navigation.

